-- Discover Financial profit rises 7 pct
-- By Avik Das in Bangalore
-- Tue Jul 22, 2014 04:17PM EDT
-- None



July 22 (Reuters) - Credit card issuer Discovery Financial Services Inc <DFS.N> reported a 7 percent rise in quarterly profit as customers spent more using credit cards in a recovering U.S. economy.

Net income rose to $644 million, or $1.35 per share, from $602 million, or $1.20 per share, a year earlier. [ID:nBw688bgHa]